Collins has pleaded not guilty. During Tuesday's court hearing, he turned his head from the screen as prosecutors showed images of Robert Middleton's badly burned body.

Defense attorney E. Tay Bond said that, just as there wasn't enough evidence in 1998 to hold Collins, there also isn't now. He has accused the Middleton's attorney of making up the rape theory.

Robert Middleton endured years of physical therapy before he died in 2011 from skin cancer.

His death was ruled a homicide because the burns were almost exclusively to blame for the cancer.

